title: ComicPirates Weeklies Index (CPWI) (2012-04 - 2015-06) (N=131k)
description:
CONTAINS:       Plaintext indeces for all Weeklies (and occasional other Timelies)
                posted from TPB accounts <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/user/shipj" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/user/shipj</a>  and
               <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/user/shipjolly" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/user/shipjolly</a>  as well as from KAT account
               <a href=" http://gesserit.000space.com/meta/kat/user/shipjolly" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://gesserit.000space.com/meta/kat/user/shipjolly</a>  with a global
                coverage of well above 90% of all English (and a few non-English)
                comics released via the "official" channels since April 2012.

DETAILS:        First = 2012-04-11   |   Last = 2015-06-24   |   Count = 131,115

FORMATTING:     The original data stems directly from the contents of the metadata
                files (see <a href=" https://thepiratebay.vg/torrent/12085049" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> https://thepiratebay.vg/torrent/12085049</a>  ), and was
                automatically processed into the following standardized format.

   |t>14-09-10 0000|s> 912,274,022|n>Spacehawk (2012) (Digital) (Bean-Empire).cbz

   t(imestamp)  two digits each for year, month, day, hour, minute of release. The
                last two are always 00, functioning only as placeholders here.

   (file)s(ize) in bytes, formatted for improved legibility. Fixed-width field with
                a 10-gigabyte maximum, which should suffice for a while yet!

   (file)n(ame) including filetype extension.

ORGANIZATION:   The three contained files are each sorted by a combination of two
                of the three fields - by name then time (filename suffix "by nt"),
                by size then name ("by sn"), and by time then name ("by tn")
